{"tid":2119714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件好尷尬既事","createTime":"2020-07-22T08:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T09:14:34.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"540a66d7dfc5662ff08ba4d07082238d777b0eb4","tid":2119714,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n是咁的，好多年前成家人去朋友屋企食飯<br />\n食完落樓下走見到個明星同佢屋企人係側邊出來<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:細佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:明星<br />\n<br />\n當時個反應係<br />\n<br />\n我:呢個好似邊個來<br />\n細佬：咪講亞視個個<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(個陣好少睇戲唔熟明星)<br />\nload左一陣先諗到邊個來<br />\n<br />\n老母：啊!<br />\n我同細佬：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明星：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勿相認"},{"pid":"d24682873444e0cdc2b7393e340c89e1f50532c2","tid":2119714,"uid":57401,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:57:26.000Z","msg":"睇完你個po"},{"pid":"d592a87adce28d72bef5248a670be393df01d791","tid":2119714,"uid":170772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"睇樓主繪聲繪色 七情上面咁講完個故事.."},{"pid":"37878917211a11ada3ef0cd2332be84f4b17503f","tid":2119714,"uid":244876,"like